{"tid":319020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4歲男孩模仿紅孩兒苦練「噴火」把床燒成炭（圖）","createTime":"2017-07-12T13:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T13:32:39.000Z","uid":20531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9094022c060cbad838d5e455842dac11ae0da9","tid":319020,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"7月4日，因為看西遊記動畫片裡的紅孩兒噴火厲害，安徽阜陽一4歲熊孩子淘淘竟然模仿片中&ldquo;噴火&rdquo;情節，在臥室打開打火機練習&ldquo;噴火&rdquo;，不慎火燒床鋪，所幸沒有人員傷亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/212156_3d4c6bb23dac866cf195ccffbbcda2c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F212156_3d4c6bb23dac866cf195ccffbbcda2c6.jpg&h=6d069c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，淘淘的父母常年在外地工作，平時他跟隨爺爺奶奶生活。 &ldquo;床墊、棉被和窗簾都被燒個精光，險些把家都燒沒了！&rdquo;提起前幾天家裡發生的火災，家住阜陽市的儲大娘至今心有餘悸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/212219_9b33fe6e9a1f9187eb157a7b6cb98e35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F212219_9b33fe6e9a1f9187eb157a7b6cb98e35.jpg&h=4a04761a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n儲大娘說，平時老兩口農活比較忙，顧不上孫子。孫子放假後天天看動畫片，以前在家也玩打火機學著&ldquo;噴火&rdquo;，被他們發現後批評教育過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/212231_ab171cdc1fdfc645ba214269b818bbb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F212231_ab171cdc1fdfc645ba214269b818bbb0.jpg&h=3050f710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民警表示，兒童年紀小，缺乏是非辨識能力。他覺得電視裡的情節好玩，就不考慮後果進行模仿，但是家長一定要注意防範。"},{"pid":"a13952135de51b70f8343fb74656b7155e72fbfa","tid":319020,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}